# # Spectral Proof of P = NP – Applications (Series I, Articles I.6–I.11)

**Author**: Christian Kithima  
**ORCID**: 0009-0003-3829-8519  
**GitHub**: [spectral-reduction-framework](https://github.com/christiankithimaomba-cyber/spectral-reduction-framework)

This document describes the practical consequences and algorithmic applications of the spectral proof of \(P = NP\) (Series I). The proof itself is given in Articles I.1–I.5. The present articles (I.6–I.11) explore the impact on cryptography, the universality of the spectral method, and concrete solutions to classic problems.

